      <title>预算协议有望达成 法债市场风险进一步下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/french-bond-market-risk-falls-further-on-hopes-of-budget-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国政府债券连续第四天上涨，推动该国债券的风险溢价降至两周多以来的最低水平，因为市场猜测该国分裂的议会最终将就预算达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/french-bond-market-risk-falls-further-on-hopes-of-budget-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 09:19:14 GMT</pubDate>
