      <title>马里挤压金矿开采商，巴里克海盗老板面临考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/barrick-s-buccaneering-boss-tested-as-mali-squeezes-gold-miners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·布里斯托花了三十年时间，穿越内战和政变，建造了非洲一些最富有的金矿，但现在巴里克黄金公司的老板却遭到急需现金的马里军政府的胁迫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/barrick-s-buccaneering-boss-tested-as-mali-squeezes-gold-miners</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 09:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非航空首席执行官称无法承受飞行员罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/south-african-airways-unable-to-sustain-pilots-strike-ceo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于大部分飞行员因薪资问题罢工，南非航空公司取消了约 60% 的航班，该航空公司负责人表示，该公司刚刚起步的财务复苏进程中将无法承受更多干扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/south-african-airways-unable-to-sustain-pilots-strike-ceo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 09:02:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚正就延长俄罗斯天然气协议进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/serbia-in-talks-to-extend-russian-natural-gas-deal-beyond-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚正在与俄罗斯进行谈判，延长将于 3 月到期的天然气供应合同，目标供应量与目前与 Gazprom PJSC 签订的协议中的供应量相似。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/serbia-in-talks-to-extend-russian-natural-gas-deal-beyond-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 05:51:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度提高非居民利率以阻止卢比贬值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/india-takes-steps-to-attract-more-inflows-to-stem-rupee-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行表示，将允许银行提高居住在海外的印度人的存款利率，以通过吸引外汇来阻止卢比下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/india-takes-steps-to-attract-more-inflows-to-stem-rupee-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 05:17:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
